]\n|referee = Attilio Soliani\n|result = D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 21 January 1940\n|round=16\n|team1 = [[Juventus]]\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score = 1-0\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2732/\n|location = [[Torino]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Olimpico Grande Torino|Stadio Benito Mussolini]]\n|referee = Giuseppe Scarpi\n|goals1 = [[Guglielmo Gabetto|Gabetto]] {{Goal|8}}\n|goals2 =\n|result=L\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 28 January 1940\n|round=17\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = [[Venezia F.C.|Venezia]]\n|score = 2-1\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2826/\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = Giacomo Bertolio\n|goals1 = [[Umberto Guarnieri|Guarnieri]] {{Goal|10||70}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|18}} [[Giovanni Alberti (calciatore)|Alberti]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 4 February 1940\n|round=18\n|team1 = [[S.S.C. Napoli|Napoli]]\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score = 0-1\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2892/\n|location = [[Napoli]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Partenopeo]]\n|referee = Raffaele Scorzoni\n|goals1 =\n|goals2 = {{Goal|78}} [[Umberto Guarnieri|Guarnieri]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 11 February 1940\n|round=19\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = Liguria\n|score = 1-0\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2754/\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = Giovanni Galeati\n|goals1 = [[Attilio Demar\u00eda|Demar\u00eda]] {{Goal|43}}\n|goals2 =\n|result=W\n}}\n\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 18 February 1940\n|round=20\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = Bari\n|score = 0-0\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2828/\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = Giacomo Bertolio\n|goals1 = \n|result=D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 25 February 1940\n|round=21\n|team1 = [[A.S. Roma|Roma]]\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score = 1-2\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2908/\n|location = [[Rome|Roma]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Nazionale|Stadio Nazionale del PNF]]\n|referee = Raffaele Scorzoni\n|goals1 = [[Luciano Alghisi|Alghisi]] {{Goal|36}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|65}} [[Annibale Frossi|Frossi]]<br />{{Goal|84}} [[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 10 March 1940\n|round=22\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = Triestina\n|score = 5-1\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2778/\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = Oreste Dellarole\n|goals1 = [[Enrico Candiani|Candiani]] {{Goal|25||36}}<br />[[Umberto Guarnieri|Guarnieri]] {{Goal|41||79}}<br />[[Giuseppe Grezar|Grezar]] {{Goal|85|aut.}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|15}} [[Mario Tosolini|Tosolini]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 17 March 1940\n|round=23\n|team1 = Modena\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score = 1-2\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2844/\n|location = [[Modena]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Alberto Braglia|Stadio Cesare Marzari]]\n|referee = Generoso Dattilo\n|goals1 = [[Raggio Montanari|Montanari]] {{Goal|48}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|37}} [[Annibale Frossi|Frossi]]<br />{{Goal|42}} [[Enrico Candiani|Candiani]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 24 March 1940\n|round=24\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = [[Torino F.C.|Torino]]\n|score = 5-1\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2938/\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = Mario Ciamberlini\n|goals1 = [[Enrico Candiani|Candiani]] {{Goal|1}}<br />[[Attilio Demar\u00eda|Demar\u00eda]] {{Goal|32|rig.}}<br />[[Umberto Guarnieri|Guarnieri]] {{Goal|50}}<br />[[Annibale Frossi|Frossi]] {{Goal|69}}<br />[[Aldo Campatelli|Campatelli]] {{Goal|73}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|10}} [[Federico Allasio|Allasio]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 31 March 1940\n|round=25\n|team1 = [[Fiorentina]]\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score = 0-3\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2780/\n|location = [[Firenze]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Artemio Franchi|Stadio Giovanni Berta]]\n|referee = Raffaele Scorzoni\n|goals1 =\n|goals2 = {{Goal|60}} [[Pietro Rebuzzi|Rebuzzi I]]<br />{{Goal|63}} [[Annibale Frossi|Frossi]]<br />{{Goal|76}} [[Aldo Campatelli|Campatelli]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 21 April 1940\n|round=26\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = [[Genoa Cricket and Football Club|Genova]]\n|score = 2-1\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2866/\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = Ferruccio Bonivento\n|goals1 = [[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]] {{Goal|43}}<br />[[Attilio Demar\u00eda|Demar\u00eda]] {{Goal|55}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|3}} [[Mario Genta|Genta]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 12 May 1940\n|round=27\n|team1 = [[Milano]]\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score = 1-3\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2940/\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio San Siro|Campo San Siro]]\n|referee = Rinaldo Barlassina\n|goals1 = [[Aldo Boffi|Boffi]] {{Goal|81|pen}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|41}} [[Enrico Candiani|Candiani]]<br />{{Goal|64|pen}} [[Attilio Demar\u00eda|Demar\u00eda]]<br />{{Goal|83}} [[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 19 May 1940\n|round=28\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = [[S.S. Lazio|Lazio]]\n|score = 4-0\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2806/\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = Giuseppe Scarpi\n|goals1 = [[Giorgio Barsanti|Barsanti]] {{Goal|32||67}}<br />[[Attilio Demar\u00eda|Demar\u00eda]] {{Goal|36}}<br />[[Annibale Frossi|Frossi]] {{Goal|37}}\n|goals2 =\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 26 May 1940\n|round=29\n|team1 = Novara\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score = 1-0\n|report =http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2876/\n|location = [[Novara]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Enrico Patti|Stadio Littorio]]\n|referee = Mario Ciamberlini\n|goals1 = [[Renato Calzolai|Calzolai]] {{Goal|81}}\n|goals2 =\n|result=L\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 2 June 1940\n|round=30\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = [[Bologna F.C.|Bologna]]\n|score = 1-0\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1939/2956/\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio San Siro|Campo San Siro]]\n|referee = Generoso Dattilo\n|goals1 = [[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]] {{Goal|9}}\n|goals2 =\n|result = W\n}}\n\n==== Coppa Italia ====\n{{main|1939\u201340 Coppa Italia}}\n==== Round of 32 ====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 24 December 1939\n|round=\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = [[Torino F.C.|Torino]]\n|score = 1-2\n|report=\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = Giuseppe Zelocchi\n|goals1 = [[Umberto Guarnieri|Guarnieri]] {{Goal|73}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|63}} [[Ermes Borsetti|Borsetti]]<br />{{Goal|81}} [[Emilio Capri|Capri]]\n|result=L\n}}\n\n== Statistics ==\n=== Squad statistics ===\n<div style=\"font-size:90%\">\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;margin:auto;clear:both;text-align:center;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Competition<ref>{{cite book|publisher=Panini|title=Almanacco Calcio 1940|p=102}}</ref>\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Points\n! colspan=\"6\" | Home\n! colspan=\"6\" | Away\n! colspan=\"6\" | Total\n! rowspan=\"2\" | [[Goal average|GD]]\n|-\n! {{Descrizione comando|G|Games}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|W|Won}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|D|Draw}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|L|Lost}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|Gs|Goals scored}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|Ga|Goals against}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|G|Games}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|W|Won}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|D|Draw}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|L|Lost}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|Gs|Goals scored}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|Ga|Goals against}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|G|Games}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|W|Won}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|D|Draw}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|L|Lost}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|Gs|Goals scored}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|Ga