 Athletic Club 1-0 FC Barcelona], [[La Liga]]</ref> with video footage of the incident inconclusive.<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4G1HT35TtTk?t=2m12 Copa del Rey | Cuartos de final | Athletic Club 1-0 FC Barcelona], [[Real Federaci\u00f3n Espa\u00f1ola de F\u00fatbol]] YouTube, 6 February 2020</ref>}}||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||34||9{{efn|name=cup20}}\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!185!!40!!23!!11{{efn|name=cup20}}!!30!!7!!238!!58{{efn|name=cup20}}\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!235!!68!!23!!11{{efn|name=cup20}}!!30!!7!!288!!86{{efn|name=cup20}}\n|}\n{{notelist}}\n\n==Honours==\n'''Spain U21'''\n*[[UEFA European Under-21 Championship]] runner-up: [[2017 UEFA European Under-21 Championship|2017]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/40451698|title=Germany U21 1\u20130 Spain U21|publisher=BBC Sport|date=30 June 2017|accessdate=6 September 2019}}</ref>\n\n'''Individual'''\n*[[La Liga Player of the Month]]: [[2018\u201319 La Liga|January 2019]]<ref name=POTM19/>\n*Golden Goal of the Season: 2018\u201319<ref name=GOTS/>\n\n==See also==\n*[[Afro-Spaniard]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Athletic Bilbao profile|id=2233/williams}}\n*{{BDFutbol|202397}}\n*{{NFT|64459}}\n\n{{Athletic Bilbao squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Williams, Inaki}}\n[[Category:1994 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Spanish people of Ghanaian descent]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Bilbao]]\n[[Category:Spanish footballers]]\n[[Category:Basque footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:La Liga players]]\n[[Category:Segunda Divisi\u00f3n B players]]\n[[Category:Tercera Divisi\u00f3n players]]\n[[Category:CD Basconia footballers]]\n[[Category:Bilbao Athletic footballers]]\n[[Category:Athletic Bilbao footballers]]\n[[Category:Spain under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Spain international footballers]]\n[[Category:Basque Country international footballers]]\n", "name_user": "Quite A Character", "label": "safe", "co